{"tid":2354574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日個foodpanda哥哥被指偷外賣袋或被控襲警","createTime":"2021-01-05T14:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T15:55:43.000Z","uid":343629,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"233e3c6030690ad70b3eea409fa235e3969b8b88","tid":2354574,"uid":343629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"警方執法手法再度惹起民憤。一名背上FoodPanda外賣袋的男子上周六在天水圍被數名軍裝員截查，軍裝警發現其銀包貼有「光時」貼紙，先恫嚇事主「而家有條《國安法》」，又質疑事主的外賣袋是「偷返嚟」，要求事主自證清白，最終將事主帶返警署。警方指，該男子涉盜竊及襲警被捕。有區議員說，事主扣留期間因情緒問題送院，至本周一獲准保釋。FoodPanda證實，片段中被捕者為其公司的自僱送遞員。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">警稱事主情緒激動涉襲警 或落案起訴</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n天水連線、元朗區議員伍健偉回覆《蘋果》時說，當天曾往現場了解事件，事主最終被帶返天水圍警署調查，及後一度警方向他表示，事主因情緒激動，涉在警署內襲警，警告會將被落案起訴襲警。惟事主被扣留至昨天（4日）上午獲准保釋，未有被告襲警。<br />\n<br />\n-蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/D5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FD5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=cd15a521\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FD5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y%2F&h=571a2511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/D5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"abf9c422d4861614dae11a01e471eb58db941365","tid":2354574,"uid":171088,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"呢隻狗既往績<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d82334586cf81c18206bade4b38676439dba0d8","tid":2354574,"uid":343629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abf9c422d4861614dae11a01e471eb58db941365","tid":2354574,"uid":171088,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"呢隻狗既往績<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:41: